('58249','20393','5','Exclusive luxury villa at private 9-hole golf course'),
('58250','20394','5','This luxury country house with panoramic views to the beautiful surrounding landscape is located at a private 9-hole golf course with golf hotel. The comfortable villa is equipped tastefully and satisfies the most discerning demands according to construction materials and technology. It was built in 2006 by a German constructor. The established garden with native plants and trees, the pool with pool house and the elevated position of the property guarantee absolute privacy.\r\nThe partly furnished country house has a living space of about 500 m² and offers a cozy living room with fireplace, country kitchen and  two bedrooms with en suite bathrooms on the ground floor. Going upstairs there are two more bedrooms with bathrooms en suite. Furthermore, the property boasts a separate guest apartment (consists of living room with kitchen, bedroom and bathroom) and a guest room with bathroom, right at the pool house. The amenities include: under floor heating (oil / water), air conditioning h / c and several covered and open terraces.\r\nThe buyer can play for free on the golf course. Furthermore, you can benefit from the hotels’ facilities such as tennis court, sauna, massage, gourmet restaurant, driving range, putting green, chipping, fitness room, 24 hour concierge service, airport limousine service, heliport, cleaning service and childcare (some of them for free).\r\nThis is the perfect home to enjoy your vacation at the highest standard. At the moment there are 3 villas for sale, have also a look at the ref. 7512, 7513 and 7514.'),
